<!--
>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>CONDITIONAL STATEMENT:
if (condition){}
else if (condition){}
else{}
switch
>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>LOOPING STAEMENTS:
single action multiple times of iteration
1.initilization
2.condition
3.iteration
4.statements

syntax:
initialization
while(condition){
    statements;
    iteration;
}

initialization
do{
    statements;
    iteration;
}while(condition);

for(initialization;condition;iteration){
    statements;
}


CAMELCASE CONVENTION: getElementById()
